  "body" : "<p>I have a table in Postgre Database. The table has 2 timestamp format columns. I need those rows where one column timestamp is not equals the second column timestamp.</p>\n<p>For the below query I need the Hibernate criteria restrictions:</p>\n<pre class=\"lang-sql prettyprint-override\"><code>select * from A where column1&lt;&gt;column2\n</code></pre>\n"
